### Variables
@host = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@idempotencyKey = {{$guid}}

### Login to get token
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### ─── T02-24: 发布快照 API ───

### 列出发布快照（分页）
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/snapshots?tableKey=orders&pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取单个快照详情
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/snapshots/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取最新快照
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/snapshots/latest?tableKey=orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 快照 diff
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/snapshots/diff?tableKey=orders&fromVersion=1&toVersion=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建发布快照
POST {{host}}/api/v1/schema/snapshots
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "tableKey": "orders",
  "publishNote": "Initial schema publish"
}

### ─── T02-25: 兼容性检查 API ───

### 兼容性检查（添加字段 + 删除字段）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/schema/compatibility-check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "tableKey": "orders",
  "addFields": [
    {
      "name": "new_status",
      "displayName": "New Status",
      "fieldType": "String",
      "length": 50,
      "allowNull": true,
      "isPrimaryKey": false,
      "isAutoIncrement": false,
      "isUnique": false,
      "sortOrder": 10
    }
  ],
  "updateFields": null,
  "removeFields": ["old_field"],
  "addIndexes": null,
  "removeIndexes": null
}

### ─── T02-26: DDL 预览 API ───

### DDL 预览
POST {{host}}/api/v1/schema/ddl-preview
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "tableKey": "orders",
  "addFields": [
    {
      "name": "total_amount",
      "displayName": "Total Amount",
      "fieldType": "Decimal",
      "precision": 18,
      "scale": 2,
      "allowNull": false,
      "isPrimaryKey": false,
      "isAutoIncrement": false,
      "isUnique": false,
      "defaultValue": "0",
      "sortOrder": 5
    }
  ],
  "removeFields": null,
  "addIndexes": [
    {
      "name": "ix_orders_total_amount",
      "isUnique": false,
      "fields": ["total_amount"]
    }
  ]
}

### ─── 依赖图 ───

### 查询表的依赖关系图
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/dependencies/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ─── 影响分析 ───

### 查询 Schema 变更影响
GET {{host}}/api/v1/schema/impact/orders?removingFields=old_field,legacy_col
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
